query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ct mc) NoMergeJoin(ct mc t) */ select min(mc.note) AS production_note,
min(t.title) AS movie_title,
min(t.production_year) AS movie_year
from company_type AS ct
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' AND mc.note not like '%(as Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer Pictures)%'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008;
